  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink240-kilavi">talaimakaṟkup puṟattoḻukkam uḷatāṉamai yaṟintu talaimakaṭ pulantavaḻi yavaṉ ataṉai yillai yeṉṟu maṟaittāṉākat tōḻi colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante told the hero when the heroine, knowing that he had “outside-conduct” (i.e., lived with concubines), became vexed, and he concealed it, saying, “That is not [the case].”
          
        </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink240">
<l>aṟiyē mallē maṟintaṉa mātō</l>
<l>poṟivaric ciṟaiya vaṇṭiṉa moyppac</l>
<l>cānta nāṟu naṟiyōḷ</l>
<l>kūnta ṉāṟuniṉ mārpē teyyō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>It is not that we do not know. We knew, did we not?</l>
        <l rend="space">Your chest is fragrant with the tresses</l>
        <l>of the fragrant woman scented with sandalwood,</l>
        <l>as swarms of bees with spots and lines on their wings hover.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
